    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you would make an attack with the attack action, you may declare a <em><strong>Homerun</strong></em>. When you do so, you may spend any additional attack you would make with the attack action, your bonus action, or your reaction. For every action or attack spent, increase the critical threat range and damage die by 1. If you score a critical hit, they're pushed back by 10*[your proficiency bonus] feet.</p>",
